*klive-0.28 (14 Apr 2007)

  14 Apr 2007; Charlie Shepherd <masterdriverz@gentoo.org>
  files/klive.init.d, metadata.xml, -klive-0.16.ebuild, -klive-0.23.ebuild,
  +klive-0.28.ebuild:
  Clean out old ebuilds, bump to 0.28 and clean out old non-working ebuilds.
  Also fix the init script for later baselayouts. Thanks to Haplo and Jakub,
  bugs 162402 and 161320. Add myself explicitly to metadata since I use this
  package.

  28 Jan 2007; Marius Mauch <genone@gentoo.org> klive-0.16.ebuild,
  klive-0.23.ebuild:
  Replacing einfo with elog

  15 Dec 2006; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> klive-0.23.ebuild:
  Marked ~hppa.

